  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      580.58,
      554.78,
      637.94
    ],
    "text": "The Intertropical Convergence Zone (where winds from the Northern Hemisphere and Southern Hemisphere converge) affects the island\u2019s weather. As a result, an increase in rainfall is expected over the island after 6 May.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.119999885559082,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      641.99,
      555.07,
      715.25
    ],
    "text": "For tomorrow: Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in the Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, North-western, Uva and Eastern provinces and in Polonnaruwa, Galle, Matara and Mullaitivu districts after 2.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      717.77,
      555.09,
      750.31
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Galle and Matara districts.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      753.61,
      554.99,
      789.67
    ],
    "text": "Showers will occur in the Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Puttalam, Galle and Matara districts during the morning too.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      792.97,
      555.16,
      830.47
    ],
    "text": "Fairly strong winds of about (30-40) kmph can be expected at times over Northern and North-central provinces and in Hambantota district.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      833.56,
      555.17,
      869.86
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central and Uva provinces and in Ampara district during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      9.119999885559082,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      873.16,
      554.36,
      944.28
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
